These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, mirinda, soy-milk
There 3 different types of food: lemon, plum, spinach
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, reading, skydiving
3 different pets are kept: horse, fish, rat
House: modern, cape-cod, palace
3 different games are played: billiard, poker, chess
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: tennis, water-polo, weightlifting
 1. the person who's sport is tennis is the person playing poker##1
 2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the owner of the rat##1
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person playing chess and the person drinking mirinda##2
 4. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 5. the owner of the fish is the person eating spinach##1
 6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person playing billiard##1
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
 8. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the modern house##1
 9. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
10. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Beverage      | mirinda    | soy-milk   | 7up           |
| Food          | plum       | spinach    | lemon         |
| Hobby         | reading    | skydiving  | hiking        |
| Pet           | horse | fish   | rat      |
| House   | cape-cod        | palace    | modern       |
| Game   | poker     | billiard  | chess       |
| Sport         | tennis     | water-polo | weightlifting |

