.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-2::.
City: boston, edinburgh, paris
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, amaryllis, begonia
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, disaster
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, punk, rock
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, british, dutch
3 different games are played: monopoly, snooker, go
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, water-polo, weightlifting
 1. the person playing go is the british##1
 2. the person playing go is the person watching disaster movies##1
 3. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
 4. the person who's sport is baseball is between the person traveling to edinburgh and the person traveling to boston##2
 5. the dutch is on the far left##1
 6. the person traveling to edinburgh is the fan of metal##1
 7. the fan of punk is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 8. the person who growsazalea is the person watching adventure movies##1
 9. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the fan of rock##1
10. the person playing go is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| City      | boston   | paris    | edinburgh         |
| Flower          | azalea    | amaryllis | begonia          |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure  | disaster  | animation     |
| Music-Genre   | rock       | punk      | metal         |
| Nationality   | dutch      | british   | australian    |
| Game           | monopoly        | go      | snooker         |
| Sport         | water-polo | baseball  | weightlifting |

