.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-3::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: ivory, chestnut, fuchsia
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, magic-tricks, skydiving
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, satire, spy
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, hot-chocolate
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, indian, russian
3 different pets are kept: hamster, hedgehog, mouse
3 different games are played: snooker, domino, chess
 1. the person who likes chestnut is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 2. the russian is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 3. the person watching adventure movies is the person who likes fuchsia##1
 4. the person watching satire movies is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 5. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing chess##1
 6. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person playing chess##1
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the indian and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
 8. the indian is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 9. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
10. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
11. the indian is the person who likes fuchsia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |
| Color          | fuchsia      | chestnut      | ivory      |
| Hobby         | fishing   | skydiving | magic-tricks |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | satire    | spy          |
| Beverage   | fanta       | cola      | hot-chocolate          |
| Nationality   | indian    | egyptian  | russian      |
| Pet           | hamster   | hedgehog  | mouse        |
| Game         | snooker  | domino   | chess     |

