.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-4::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, milk, soy-milk
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, fishing, sudoku
The people have 3 different jobs:  musician, security-guard, social-worker
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, sports
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, dunhill, baccarat
There are 3 different favourite colors: grey, white, blood-red
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, june, may
 1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who likes blood-red##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
 4. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
 5. the alhambra-smoker is between the person watching disaster movies and the person drinking almond-milk##2
 6. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 7. the alhambra-smoker is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 8. the musician is the person who's birthday is in may##1
 9. the person drinking milk is between the musician and the social-worker##2
10. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person who likes white##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |       3       |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | milk           | soy-milk      |
| Hobby         | chess       | sudoku         | fishing       |
| Job           | musician    | security-guard | social-worker |
| Movie-Genre   | crime       | sports         | disaster      |
| Cigar   | baccarat         | alhambra        | dunhill          |
| Color   | blood-red   | white       | grey         |
| Birthday           | may       | february         | june        |

