3 different pets are kept: horse, mouse, snake
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, fonseca, bluemaster
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, quad-bike, taxi
 1. the person eating onion is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 2. the person driving the bike is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
 3. the person drinking water is the bluemaster-smoker##1
 4. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
 5. the bluemaster-smoker is between the fonseca-smoker and the person who likes fuchsia##2
 6. the bluemaster-smoker is between the dannemann-smoker and the owner of the snake##2
 7. the person driving the bike is between the person eating strawberry and the person drinking 7up##2
 8. the person who likes red is on the right of the person who likes green##1
 9. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who likes green##1
10. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person eating strawberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |     3      |
| Beverage      | 7up          | water         | juice      |
| Food          | eggplant     | onion         | strawberry |
| Hobby           | skydiving | board-games    | dancing   |
