.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-18::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: rose, sunflower, balloon-flower
There 3 different types of food: broccoli, mango, pumpkin
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, hiking, singing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, blues, techno
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, rosesy, mystery
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, siglo, blend
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, ship, skateboard
1. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the fan of techno##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
3. the person eating mango is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
4. the pall-mall-smoker is between the person watching epic movies and the fan of blues##2
5. the person eating pumpkin is between the fan of techno and the person who's hobby is singing##2
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
7. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
8. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
9. the person watching rosesy movies is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
